1. *Skupa* smo otišli u park. (We went to the park together.)
2. On je svoju odluku donio *skupa* sa drugovima. (He made his decision together with his friends.)
3. Rešili smo da odlučimo *skupa*. (We decided to decide together.)
4. *Skupa* smo se složili da je to prava stvar. (We agreed together that it was the right thing to do.)
5. Svi smo bili *skupa* na proslavi. (We were all together at the celebration.)